-related lists|Bands]]\n", "text_old": "{{refimprove|date=October 2014}}\n{{use mdy dates|date=January 2013}}\n\nThis article contains a list of bands formed in [[New York City]], [[New York (state)|New York]].  Bands should be notable and linked to their articles which lists their New York origins in the lead.  References should be provided for any new entries on this list.  Bands may be temporarily [[red-linked]] (while an article is developed) as long as the reference establishes that the band is notable and from New York.\n\n{{dynamic list|date=January 2013}}\n{{col-begin|3}}\n{{col-break}}\n\n==#==\n* [[24-7 Spyz]]\n* [[2 in a Room]]\n\n==A&ndash;F==\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n* [[A Place To Bury Strangers]]\n* [[Alice Donut]]\n* [[AJR (band)]]\n* [[American Classical Orchestra]]\n* [[American Composers Orchestra]]\n* [[The Amygdaloids]]\n* [[The Antlers (band)|The Antlers]]\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]]\n* [[Axolotl (band)]]\n* [[Bad Ronald (band)|Bad Ronald]]\n* [[Band of Susans]]\n* [[Barkmarket]]\n* [[Battles (band)|Battles]]\n* [[Beach Fossils]]\n* [[Beastie Boys]]\n* [[Blitzspeer]]\n* [[Blondie (band)|Blondie]]\n*[[Blood, Sweat & Tears]]<ref>http://www.allmusic.com/artist/blood-sweat-tears-mn0000046925/biography</ref>\n* [[Bloodsimple]]\n* [[Bloody Panda]]\n* [[The Blue Flames]]\n* [[Blue \u00d6yster Cult]]\n* [[Blues Magoos]]\n* [[Boys Choir of Harlem]]\n* [[Brand New (band)|Brand New]]\n* [[The Brandos]]\n* [[Breakfast Club (band)|Breakfast Club]]\n* [[Brutal Truth]]\n* [[The Cake]]\n* [[The Candles]]\n* [[Castevet]]\n* [[Certain General]]\n* [[Chairlift (band)]]\n* [[The Chiffons]]\n* [[Circus Mort]]\n* [[The City and Horses]]\n* [[Class Actress]]\n* [[The Coachmen]]\n* [[The Cold Crush Brothers]]\n* [[Company Flow]]\n* [[Contre]]\n* [[The Cro-Mags]]\n* [[The Crystals]]\n* [[The Crystals]]\n* Dark Sky Hustlers\n* [[The Davenports]]\n* [[Deee-Lite]]\n* [[Defunkt]]\n* [[De La Soul]]\n* [[DeLeon (band)|DeLeon]]\n* [[The Dictators]]\n* [[DIIV]]\n